      "role": "user",
      "content": "a home kit?? that sounds expensive. i saw some people online saying that if you feel the tremors it's just because your electrolytes are off and you just need to take more salt or something. if i just stay super hydrated and eat more salty snacks, won't that balance it out and stop the shakiness without me needing a real blood test? i really just want to fix this myself.",
